15:15.347 --> 15:16.713
I'm not saying
                     go to Peru,

15:16.848 --> 15:18.315
but don't rule
                       Peru out.

15:18.382 --> 15:20.017
Will you stop this?

15:20.085 --> 15:21.251
There's no way in the world

15:21.319 --> 15:22.786
you're gonna get me
     to be afraid of this.

15:22.854 --> 15:24.354
I happen to be
      a realistic person.

15:24.422 --> 15:27.357
I always have been,
     and I always will be.

15:27.425 --> 15:28.859
Nobody's trying
                   to scare you.

15:28.927 --> 15:30.327
Another one.

15:30.394 --> 15:32.162
We're just
                  trying to say,

15:32.264 --> 15:34.531
that as sure as there's
                a God in heaven,

15:34.599 --> 15:37.400
you're going belly up
                at 7:00 tonight.

15:37.468 --> 15:39.536
Unless you're not
              in your apartment.

15:39.604 --> 15:42.306
Look, just let me say this.

15:42.374 --> 15:44.808
I don't believe in
       any of this stuff.

15:44.876 --> 15:45.876
But as a matter of fact,

15:45.944 --> 15:47.811
I'm not gonna be
    at my apartment at 7:00,

15:47.846 --> 15:50.247
because I'm going out on a date
with a wonderful woman.

15:50.314 --> 15:51.348
See?

15:51.415 --> 15:52.616
Now is anybody, uh,

15:52.684 --> 15:54.484
foolish enough to be relieved
by any of that?

15:54.552 --> 15:57.821
(overlapping chatter)

15:57.889 --> 15:59.189
All right, that's
                  good planning.

15:59.257 --> 16:01.391
I didn't plan that.

16:01.459 --> 16:03.560
Now if you'll excuse me,
  I'm a little late. Good-bye.

16:03.595 --> 16:04.928
ALL:
Good-bye, Alex.

16:04.963 --> 16:06.797
(overlapping chatter)

16:07.833 --> 16:09.833
(phone ringing)

16:15.573 --> 16:17.507
(grunting)

16:20.812 --> 16:22.712
Cabbie cooties.

16:25.183 --> 16:27.717
Sunshine Cab.

16:27.853 --> 16:29.786
He just walked out the door.

16:29.788 --> 16:32.756
Can I take a message?

16:33.859 --> 16:35.759
Oh, you're the dame

16:35.794 --> 16:38.795
that Reiger's gonna date
         tonight, huh?

16:38.864 --> 16:40.797
No!

16:40.866 --> 16:43.300
No, no, no, no,
       you can't do that.

16:43.368 --> 16:45.302
No, you gotta go out with him.

16:45.370 --> 16:48.305
What reason could you have
 for breaking a date with him?

16:49.774 --> 16:53.710
You got a 104 degree temperature
    and projectile vomiting?

16:55.613 --> 16:58.548
He's had worse dates.

16:59.851 --> 17:01.818
All right, all right.

17:01.820 --> 17:04.820
I'll save the man myself.

17:06.057 --> 17:07.958
Reiger!

17:26.010 --> 17:27.944
(knocking on door)

17:28.012 --> 17:29.446
Yeah.

17:29.513 --> 17:32.416
Yeah, hold on.

17:32.517 --> 17:33.383
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

17:33.451 --> 17:34.651
Come on, Reiger, we gotta
                get out of here.

17:34.719 --> 17:35.819
What are you
talking about?
                   Come on.

17:35.920 --> 17:37.154
Peggy called,

17:37.222 --> 17:39.189
she can't go out and
            you can't stay here.

17:39.257 --> 17:40.824
Come on, we'll go down
                 to 42nd street,

17:40.892 --> 17:42.259
look at weirdos and
            have a cheeseburger.

17:42.294 --> 17:43.561
No, wait a minute.

17:43.628 --> 17:44.795
Wait, wait a minute.

17:44.862 --> 17:46.630
Why can't she make it?
           Forget it, forget it,

17:46.698 --> 17:48.898
being dumped on by a dame is
     the least of your problems.

17:48.966 --> 17:50.434
You've got the Grim
          Reaper to worry about.

17:50.501 --> 17:51.569
We'll go to a movie.
Louie,

17:51.670 --> 17:53.037
will you stop this?
                        Come on.

17:53.104 --> 17:54.438
I'm not gonna go anywhere.

17:55.574 --> 17:57.641
Reiger, the dream's
coming true.

17:57.708 --> 17:59.976
You're here in your apartment,
it's Thursday night,

18:00.045 --> 18:01.978
it's almost 7:00.

18:02.080 --> 18:03.647
All right, look.

18:03.714 --> 18:04.981
All right.
                      (laughing)

18:05.050 --> 18:07.884
I admit your life is nothing
to jump up and down about.

18:08.019 --> 18:10.854
But it must mean
something to you.

18:10.922 --> 18:12.489
Oh, and you think all
       those other things

18:12.557 --> 18:13.624
have come true, huh?

18:13.691 --> 18:15.058
Like drinking a glass
       of water quickly,

18:15.126 --> 18:16.693
being mistaken for a girl?

18:16.761 --> 18:18.495
Dancing the cancan
                in a green shirt

18:18.597 --> 18:20.030
and a catcher's
                           mask.

18:20.065 --> 18:22.166
Oh, and at 7:00,
       precisely at 7:00,

18:22.233 --> 18:24.702
there's a knock at the door,
  and who's on the other side?

18:24.769 --> 18:25.702
Death is on...

18:25.770 --> 18:27.471
(coughing):
                        Death...

18:27.539 --> 18:28.638
Excuse me.

18:28.706 --> 18:30.640
(coughing continues)

18:32.810 --> 18:35.879
(coughing):
That's the silliest
thing I ever heard.

18:35.947 --> 18:37.314
Aha!

18:37.382 --> 18:40.284
Ah-ha-ha-ha!

18:40.385 --> 18:42.018
Ah-ho-ho-ho!

18:42.120 --> 18:43.686
Reiger!

18:43.754 --> 18:45.055
Reiger, what do you say now?

18:45.123 --> 18:47.157
Look what time it is.
       Let's get the hell

18:47.225 --> 18:48.625
out of here!
Boy, come on!

18:48.693 --> 18:50.260
I'm not leaving
                           here.
Come! Come!

18:50.295 --> 18:51.995
Out! Get out!

18:52.063 --> 18:54.064
I'm staying here tonight.
    I'm staying right here.

18:54.132 --> 18:55.165
(phone ringing)

18:55.233 --> 18:56.800
I have no intention of going...

18:59.871 --> 19:01.238
Hello?

19:01.372 --> 19:02.472
No, this is not Mary.

19:02.540 --> 19:03.941
Do I sound like a Mary?

19:04.008 --> 19:05.209
You have the wrong number.

19:05.276 --> 19:07.411
Louie, why don't you just...

19:09.447 --> 19:10.414
Mary?

19:10.481 --> 19:11.748
It's happening!

19:11.816 --> 19:13.516
It's happening!

19:13.584 --> 19:14.551
It's happening!

19:14.618 --> 19:15.986
Come on, out!

19:16.054 --> 19:17.854
Out of here.
            Louie...

19:17.922 --> 19:19.189
No, no, no, no.

19:19.257 --> 19:20.857
No, no, Louie, no, Louie.

19:20.959 --> 19:21.592
Get out!
                        No!

19:21.726 --> 19:23.160
I am not gonna leave
                 this apartment.

19:23.194 --> 19:24.428
If I walk through that door,

19:24.496 --> 19:26.463
I am violating everything
         I believe in.

19:26.531 --> 19:28.365
I'm giving up the control
        of my own life.

19:28.432 --> 19:30.134
The hell with that.

19:30.201 --> 19:31.868
I'm gonna live my future.

19:31.936 --> 19:33.437
I'm not gonna be afraid of it.

19:33.538 --> 19:36.340
Reiger, will you cut
the Joan of Arc stuff?

19:36.407 --> 19:38.342
And don't tempt fate?

19:38.344 --> 19:39.610
Tempt fate,
                          Louie?

19:39.678 --> 19:41.611
No, I'm not gonna
                     tempt fate.

19:41.680 --> 19:43.013
I'm gonna bait fate.

19:43.081 --> 19:44.314
No, no, green!
             Yeah.

19:44.382 --> 19:46.316
Rigger, no green!

19:46.384 --> 19:47.784
No. No, no, Reiger.

19:47.852 --> 19:49.286
Yeah!
        Reiger!

19:49.354 --> 19:50.720
Don't do this, Reiger.

19:50.788 --> 19:53.223
Louie, if I'm gonna die,
       I'm gonna die as I lived.

19:53.291 --> 19:55.425
Dancing the cancan in a green
  shirt and a catcher's mask.

19:55.493 --> 19:57.294
No, no, no,
     don't lift those feet.

19:57.362 --> 19:58.495
Don't, Reiger!
                     (humming)

19:58.563 --> 20:00.430
Reiger, don't do this.

20:00.498 --> 20:02.132
No, Reiger!

20:02.200 --> 20:03.567
It's coming true!

20:03.635 --> 20:05.368
The dream...

20:05.436 --> 20:08.205
(clock chiming)

20:24.823 --> 20:26.756
(whimpering)

20:32.397 --> 20:34.398
Louie...

20:34.400 --> 20:36.633
I didn't die.

20:38.503 --> 20:39.803
(chuckles)

20:42.640 --> 20:44.374
(laughing)

20:48.079 --> 20:50.747
Ignatowski's a boob.

20:53.685 --> 20:55.618
That was a nice cancan.

20:55.687 --> 20:57.620
Thank you.

20:59.624 --> 21:02.426
Now listen, Louie,
                repeat after me.

21:02.493 --> 21:04.527
Superstitions are...

21:04.595 --> 21:06.729
(knocking on door)

21:06.831 --> 21:08.532
Now you did it!

21:08.633 --> 21:10.534
I almost apologized!

21:13.204 --> 21:14.271
Don't you dare!

21:14.338 --> 21:15.638
Don't go near that door!

21:15.706 --> 21:17.307
Reiger, stay away
        from that door!

21:17.375 --> 21:18.942
Louie, I have to see what's on

21:19.010 --> 21:20.411
the other side
                   of that door.
  No! Death is on the other side

21:20.478 --> 21:21.512
of this door.
I don't care, I want to see it!

21:21.579 --> 21:22.312
No!

21:22.380 --> 21:23.280
Louie, get away from the door.
No!

21:23.348 --> 21:24.381
Get away from the door, Lou!
 No!

21:24.516 --> 21:25.282
No, no, Reiger.

21:25.416 --> 21:26.716
No, no, Reiger!
                        (grunts)

21:26.784 --> 21:29.119
No! No!
Louie, get away
from the door!

21:34.559 --> 21:35.692
(screaming)

21:51.042 --> 21:52.275
Reiger, did you see it?

21:52.343 --> 21:53.776
It was hideous!

21:56.647 --> 22:00.517
Louie, it was a little girl
     selling sugar cookies.

22:05.590 --> 22:07.524
My favorite.

22:11.629 --> 22:12.895
Here.

22:12.963 --> 22:14.831
Thanks for coming by, Lou.

22:20.438 --> 22:22.339
One for me and three for you,
              huh?

22:25.042 --> 22:26.977
Look, Reiger...

22:28.513 --> 22:31.414
...I got to make a confession.

22:32.917 --> 22:34.852
I was pretty scared there.

22:36.888 --> 22:38.755
But you...

22:38.823 --> 22:41.758
you got guts.

22:41.826 --> 22:44.060
You're a rock, Reiger.

22:44.162 --> 22:45.895
Good night, Lou.

22:45.964 --> 22:47.197
So long.

23:00.878 --> 23:03.880
Oh my God, a ghost.

23:03.915 --> 23:06.449
Jim, it's me.

23:06.584 --> 23:08.751
A talking ghost.

23:08.853 --> 23:10.721
Jim, I'm not a ghost.

23:10.788 --> 23:12.756
I didn't die.

23:12.824 --> 23:15.125
You may be a psychic,
  but you missed on this one.

23:15.259 --> 23:17.060
A reasonable ghost.

23:17.095 --> 23:18.995
Hey Jeff, give me a cab.

23:19.063 --> 23:20.897
A working ghost.

23:20.932 --> 23:21.999
Bye, Jim.

23:22.066 --> 23:23.200
Have a nice day.

23:23.234 --> 23:24.801
A courteous ghost!

23:34.979 --> 23:37.214
(theme song playing)

24:00.805 --> 24:02.105
WOMAN:
    <i>Good night, Mr. Walters!</i>

24:02.173 --> 24:03.173
(man grumbling)

